{
  "texts": [
    "Using the traditional Holt & Laury task (Hoelzemann et al., 2024), we confirm research showing how AI agents based on LLM tend to be risk-neutral as the average participant in academic lab studies (Mei et al., 2024).",
    "We also repeat the same preference elicitation task after priming AI agents with their respective risk profiles, finding that our priming significantly changes how agents respond to the Holt & Laury task in the expected direction."
  ]
}